modName: Half Nord Half Breton Female Character Preset
summary: This file gives a good-looking half Nord half Breton female character preset.
descriptionHtml:
[youtube]UmgSqNG1zGU[/youtube]Installation:
Download the file and extract it, then put the BretonLady.jslot fileÂ in the file > skyrim>Data>skse>plugins>CharGen>Presets

Uninstallation:
Delete the BretonLady.jslot directly from the skyrim>Data>skse>plugins>CharGen>Presets

NOTE: THIS CHARACTER PRESET DIDN'T APPLY ANY MAKE UP ON HER FACE, YOU CAN ADD ANY MAKE UP BY YOUR OWN THROUGH THE RACEMENU IN THE GAME AS YOU LIKE.

MAKE SURE YOU CHOOSE RACE BRETON WHEN YOU ARE USING THE RECEMENU

I will post more character preset if you guys like it.
You can also tell me in the comment what type of character you would like to see

Hope you guys enjoy!
Be sure to endorse if you liked it! Thanks! You are awesome!

For your best game experience, you may need following mods since I created the preset based on the supports of these mods
